data.description: Charming 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home nestled in the historic Frankford section of Philadelphia. This well-maintained property boasts a spacious foyer welcoming you into its warm ambiance. Straight through you'll notice and open and spacious living room and dining room perfect for hosting gatherings with loved ones. The well-appointed galley kitchen with granite countertops compliments the living space, making it ideal for entertaining. The residence features three cozy bedrooms, ideal for a growing family or accommodating guests and a stylish bathroom. With a single garage space and a two car driveway space in rear of home, parking is convenient and secure.  This home also has a large spacious basement that can be used as storage or turned into a fully renovated finished basement if desired. Enjoy the convenience of urban living while experiencing the comfort of a suburban retreat. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful home yours!
